by a topiary nightmare,

832
00:42:41,731 --> 00:42:43,994
and you want to quote
Tennyson? Down here?

833
00:42:44,168 --> 00:42:46,998
Yeah. Yeah, man.
He knew all about it.

834
00:42:47,172 --> 00:42:48,826
"Let love clasp grief," man.
Come here.

835
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:50,349
[Bernie] Mm.

836
00:42:50,523 --> 00:42:51,675
You know, humans,
we think we took

837
00:42:51,699 --> 00:42:53,918
ourselves off the food chain,

838
00:42:54,092 --> 00:42:58,139
but maybe, maybe the Titans
are here to remind us.

839
00:43:00,054 --> 00:43:01,074
I think that there is something

840
00:43:01,099 --> 00:43:02,143
seriously wrong with you.

841
00:43:03,579 --> 00:43:04,362
- Okay.
- Mm-kay.

842
00:43:04,536 --> 00:43:06,539
- Okay.
- Mm.

843
00:43:06,713 --> 00:43:08,585
- [radio beeps]
- [sighs] It's not working.

844
00:43:08,759 --> 00:43:11,065
We better move on.
We'll mourn later.

845
00:43:12,893 --> 00:43:14,373
Jia. Come on.

846
00:43:14,547 --> 00:43:15,626
- Come on, bud.
- But the...

847
00:43:15,766 --> 00:43:18,115
He was eaten by a tree.

848
00:43:18,289 --> 00:43:19,889
I don't...
I don't want to die like that.

849
00:43:20,030 --> 00:43:21,030
Not by a tree.

850
00:43:25,775 --> 00:43:27,429
[crowd screaming]

851
00:43:27,603 --> 00:43:28,692
[Godzilla growling]

852
00:43:30,867 --> 00:43:32,260
[pilot over radio] Tower,

853
00:43:32,434 --> 00:43:33,827
we can't get
any closer than this.

854
00:43:34,001 --> 00:43:37,179
Godzilla's burning hot
with radiation.

855
00:43:37,353 --> 00:43:39,528
Whatever he's headed for
