865
00:44:08,949 --> 00:44:10,710
[automated voice]
Classified file three two four.

866
00:44:10,733 --> 00:44:12,387
Titanus Tiamat.

867
00:44:12,561 --> 00:44:14,085
Titan nineteen.

868
00:44:14,259 --> 00:44:16,958
Extremely aggressive,
territorial.

869
00:44:17,132 --> 00:44:19,960
Weaponizing her body
of razor-sharp scales...

870
00:44:20,135 --> 00:44:22,527
Tiamat's Arctic lair
sits in the direct path

871
00:44:22,702 --> 00:44:25,443
