solar winds,

872
00:44:25,617 --> 00:44:29,143
making it the largest
stockpile of energy on Earth.

873
00:44:29,318 --> 00:44:32,103
If Godzilla takes down Tiamat,
he'll supercharge.

874
00:44:35,411 --> 00:44:36,411
