879
00:44:54,472 --> 00:44:56,126
[in sign language]

880
00:44:56,300 --> 00:44:58,476
Yeah.

881
00:44:58,650 --> 00:45:00,130
The markings are older
than the ones

882
00:45:00,304 --> 00:45:01,829
