consistent with the Iwi.

885
00:45:14,623 --> 00:45:16,190
[in sign language]

886
00:45:22,980 --> 00:45:24,503
[mystical music playing]

887
00:45:26,635 --> 00:45:27,637
Whoa.

888
00:45:40,693 --> 00:45:42,391
Oh, this is remarkable.

889
00:45:42,565 --> 00:45:43,958
[camera clicks]

890
00:45:51,748 --> 00:45:53,489
Now, that's weird.

891
00:45:54,882 --> 00:45:56,492
There's no moss on these ones.

892
00:46:03,541 --> 00:46:04,541
Hello.

893
00:46:10,679 --> 00:46:12,246
[Ilene] Mothra.

894
00:46:12,420 --> 00:46:15,554
[Bernie] Queen of the monsters.
In Hollow Earth.

895
00:46:15,728 --> 00:46:17,706
[Ilene] Her lineage must go
back further than we thought.

896
00:46:17,730 --> 00:46:19,166
[breathing heavily]

897
00:46:22,431 --> 00:46:23,824
[in sign language]

898
00:46:26,086 --> 00:46:27,086
Yeah.

899
00:46:27,217 --> 00:46:28,740
[insects chittering]

900
00:46:46,106 --> 00:46:47,106
No, no, no.

901
00:46:48,717 --> 00:46:51,155
