Whoa, whoa, whoa!

907
00:47:09,043 --> 00:47:13,090
[Bernie] It's like some kind of
a irrigation system. [laughs]

908
00:47:13,264 --> 00:47:14,918
Only this predates everything

909
00:47:15,092 --> 00:47:16,440
Mesopotamians, the Lemurians...

910
