- [Bernie] It just keeps going.

912
00:47:23,273 --> 00:47:25,320
- Wait, wait, wait.
- Oh. Sorry.

913
00:47:25,494 --> 00:47:27,409
[Trapper] Oh, whoa.
What the...?

914
