917
00:47:37,114 --> 00:47:38,594
Ancient alien astronauts.

918
00:47:38,768 --> 00:47:39,811
Yeah.

919
00:47:39,987 --> 00:47:41,771
[eerie music playing]

920
00:47:43,467 --> 00:47:44,730
