921
00:47:44,905 --> 00:47:46,471
The water's running underneath.

922
00:47:46,644 --> 00:47:47,907
And this is organic.

923
00:47:50,518 --> 00:47:51,518
[crackles]

924
00:47:55,610 --> 00:47:56,610
Yeah.

925
00:48:00,050 --> 00:48:02,096
Some kind of bioelectric hub.

926
00:48:06,534 --> 00:48:09,842
[Bernie chuckles]

927
00:48:10,016 --> 00:48:12,715
[Trapper] It's like camouflage.
[chuckles]

928
00:48:12,889 --> 00:48:13,889
Wow.

929
00:48:16,849 --> 00:48:18,025
[electricity crackling]

930
00:48:20,070 --> 00:48:21,766
Should she be doing that?

931
00:48:21,942 --> 00:48:23,902
She shouldn't be doing that,
right? Should she...?

932
00:48:24,509 --> 00:48:25,858
[Ilene grunting]

933
00:48:30,210 --> 00:48:32,050
- [mystical music playing]
- [Trapper chuckles]

934
00:48:33,170 --> 00:48:34,476
[enthralling music playing]

935
00:48:37,914 --> 00:48:39,697
[Ilene gasps]

936
00:48:39,871 --> 00:48:42,353
[in sign language]

937
00:48:42,527 --> 00:48:44,615
This must be
the source of the signal.

938
00:48:44,789 --> 00:48:46,356
Oh, we've gotta check this out.

939
00:48:46,530 --> 00:48:47,530
Yeah.

940
00:48:49,230 --> 00:48:50,231
[Ilene grunts]

941
00:48:51,972 --> 00:48:53,233
[Ilene] Okay. Go, go, go. Go.

942
00:48:56,106 --> 00:48:57,498
[enthralling music continues]

943
00:49:00,936 --> 00:49:02,025
