997
00:54:03,543 --> 00:54:04,980
[Tiamat screeching]

998
00:54:06,547 --> 00:54:07,635
[screeching]

999
00:54:07,809 --> 00:54:08,809
[roars]

1000
00:54:10,768 --> 00:54:12,900
