That's right.

1008
00:54:57,989 --> 00:54:59,509
[commander]
He's gone to Tiamat's lair.

1009
00:55:13,918 --> 00:55:14,963
Wait, wait, wait.

1010
00:55:19,750 --> 00:55:21,795
