Wait, what did she say?

1012
00:55:23,449 --> 00:55:24,625
She says we're not alone.

1013
00:55:24,798 --> 00:55:26,365
See? I knew it.
I knew I felt something.

1014
00:55:30,239 --> 00:55:31,239
Come on, then.

1015
