1018
00:55:38,943 --> 00:55:40,989
[Bernie] Oh, my God. [gasps]

1019
00:55:41,163 --> 00:55:42,523
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.
Oh, my God.

1020
00:55:42,643 --> 00:55:44,163
It's going away.
It's going away. Okay.

1021
00:55:50,519 --> 00:55:51,599
[suspenseful music playing]

1022
00:55:56,134 --> 00:55:58,572
[tense music playing]

1023
00:56:10,452 --> 00:56:11,846
Oh, my God.

1024
00:56:13,108 --> 00:56:14,543
Oh, my God.

1025
00:56:14,717 --> 00:56:16,764
[dramatic music playing]

1026
00:56:22,639 --> 00:56:23,639
[Ilene] What?

1027
00:56:23,813 --> 00:56:25,206
[Bernie gasps]

1028
00:56:25,380 --> 00:56:27,338
