1029
00:56:27,514 --> 00:56:28,713
protected within Hollow Earth.

1030
00:56:28,818 --> 00:56:30,298
[gasps]

1031
00:56:30,472 --> 00:56:32,016
These structures,
they look like they've been

1032
00:56:32,039 --> 00:56:34,650
