1064
00:58:59,840 --> 00:59:01,536
[soft music playing]

1065
00:59:07,369 --> 00:59:08,891
[Bernie yelps]

1066
00:59:09,065 --> 00:59:10,786
- Okay, come on. Okay.
- Let's go, let's go.

1067
00:59:14,505 --> 00:59:17,248
[bell tolling, echoes]

1068
00:59:17,422 --> 00:59:18,771
[Bernie] Whoa. Oh. [echoing]

1069
