Can I?

1070
00:59:29,913 --> 00:59:31,653
Thank you.

1071
00:59:31,827 --> 00:59:32,873
[in sign language]

1072
00:59:33,742 --> 00:59:35,527
Of course.

1073
00:59:35,702 --> 00:59:36,981
[Trapper]
What's she saying, Doc?

1074
00:59:39,096 --> 00:59:40,856
The beacon that we've been
following, it's...

1075
00:59:43,099 --> 00:59:44,710
It's the Iwi calling for help.

1076
00:59:46,190 --> 00:59:49,498
- [Trapper] Oh. Whoa.
- [Ilene gasps]

1077
00:59:57,201 --> 01:00:01,248
So, wait. They send out
this SOS, and then what?

1078
01:00:01,422 --> 01:00:02,510
Godzilla hears it?

1079
01:00:02,684 --> 01:00:05,034
Yeah. They woke him up.

1080
01:00:05,208 --> 01:00:06,775
An SOS for what?
They already live

1081
01:00:06,949 --> 01:00:08,230
in a nightmare
monster hellscape.

1082
01:00:08,298 --> 01:00:09,735
What could possibly scare them?

1083
01:00:09,909 --> 01:00:11,539
Hey. She can understand
everything that you say.

1084
01:00:11,563 --> 01:00:13,869
- She understands me?
- Oh, good.

1085
01:00:14,043 --> 01:00:15,742
And a nightmare
monster hellscape

1086
01:00:15,916 --> 01:00:18,527
