1099
01:01:29,336 --> 01:01:32,862
Hollow Earth lived in harmony
with the surface world.

1100
01:01:33,036 --> 01:01:36,518
The Titans were
the guardians of nature

1101
01:01:36,692 --> 01:01:39,826
